This should work straight out of the box, just make sure you have the correct Mongo settings, no installation necessary!


And as far as using this in public, do not do the following:
* Sell (ads on the site are fine, selling this script is not)
* Claim you wrote it all yourself

And make sure you:
* Give me attribution.
* Don't defile the code, modify, not molest.
* Tell your friends